pullRequest.body:
This PR deprecates 32 legacy semibundled `Ordered*` typeclasses and migrates to new mixin typeclasses `IsOrdered(Cancel)(Add)Monoid` and `Is(Strict)OrderedRing`.

|Old|New|
|---|---|
| `[Ordered(Add)CommMonoid Œ±]` | `[(Add)CommMonoid Œ±] [PartialOrder Œ±] [IsOrdered(Add)Monoid Œ±]` |
| `[OrderedCancel(Add)CommMonoid Œ±]` | `[(Add)CommMonoid Œ±] [PartialOrder Œ±] [IsOrderedCancel(Add)Monoid Œ±]` |
| `[LinearOrdered(Add)CommMonoid Œ±]` | `[(Add)CommMonoid Œ±] [LinearOrder Œ±] [IsOrdered(Add)Monoid Œ±]` |
| `[LinearOrderedCancel(Add)CommMonoid Œ±]` | `[(Add)CommMonoid Œ±] [LinearOrder Œ±] [IsOrderedCancel(Add)Monoid Œ±]` |
| `[Ordered(Add)CommGroup Œ±]` | `[(Add)CommGroup Œ±] [PartialOrder Œ±] [IsOrdered(Add)Monoid Œ±]` |
| `[LinearOrdered(Add)CommGroup]` | `[(Add)CommGroup Œ±] [LinearOrder Œ±] [IsOrdered(Add)Monoid Œ±]` |
| `[OrderedSemiring Œ±]` | `[Semiring Œ±] [PartialOrder Œ±] [IsOrderedRing Œ±]` |
| `[OrderedCommSemiring Œ±]` | `[CommSemiring Œ±] [PartialOrder Œ±] [IsOrderedRing Œ±]` |
| `[OrderedRing Œ±]` | `[Ring Œ±] [PartialOrder Œ±] [IsOrderedRing Œ±]` |
| `[OrderedCommRing Œ±]` | `[CommRing Œ±] [PartialOrder Œ±] [IsOrderedRing Œ±]` |
| `[StrictOrderedSemiring Œ±]` | `[Semiring Œ±] [PartialOrder Œ±] [IsStrictOrderedRing Œ±]` |
| `[StrictOrderedCommSemiring Œ±]` | `[CommSemiring Œ±] [PartialOrder Œ±] [IsStrictOrderedRing Œ±]` |
| `[StrictOrderedRing Œ±]` | `[Ring Œ±] [PartialOrder Œ±] [IsStrictOrderedRing Œ±]` |
| `[StrictOrderedCommRing Œ±]` | `[CommRing Œ±] [PartialOrder Œ±] [IsOrderedRing Œ±]` |
| `[LinearOrderedSemiring Œ±]` | `[Semiring Œ±] [LinearOrder Œ±] [IsStrictOrderedRing Œ±]` |
| `[LinearOrderedCommSemiring Œ±]` | `[CommSemiring Œ±] [LinearOrder Œ±] [IsStrictOrderedRing Œ±]` |
| `[LinearOrderedRing Œ±]` | `[Ring Œ±] [LinearOrder Œ±] [IsStrictOrderedRing Œ±]` |
| `[LinearOrderedCommRing Œ±]` | `[CommRing Œ±] [LinearOrder Œ±] [IsStrictOrderedRing Œ±]` |
| `[LinearOrderedSemifield Œ±]` | `[Semifield Œ±] [LinearOrder Œ±] [IsStrictOrderedRing Œ±]` |
| `[LinearOrderedField Œ±]` | `[Field Œ±] [LinearOrder Œ±] [IsStrictOrderedRing Œ±]` |
| `[NormedLatticeAddCommGroup Œ±]` | `[NormedAddCommGroup Œ±] [Lattice Œ±] [HasSolidNorm Œ±] [IsOrderedAddMonoid Œ±]` |
| `[NormedOrdered(Add)Group Œ±]` | `[Normed(Add)CommGroup Œ±] [PartialOrder Œ±] [IsOrdered(Add)Monoid Œ±]` |
| `[NormedLinearOrdered(Add)Group Œ±]` | `[Normed(Add)CommGroup Œ±] [LinearOrder Œ±] [IsOrdered(Add)Monoid Œ±]` |
| `[NormedLinearOrderedField Œ±]` | `[NormedField Œ±] [LinearOrder Œ±] [IsStrictOrderedRing Œ±]` |
